<section class="container-wide py-24">
  <h2 class="text-center font-display text-[var(--text-2xl)] font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">
    From 183 skills to the ones that matter
  </h2>

  <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">Point at your repo</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">Configure a GitHub plugin repo and Skillbase reads every <code class="font-mono text-[var(--accent-text)]">SKILL.md</code> manifest. Always in sync — no separate publishing step.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">See what's used</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">Track which named skills are invoked, how often, and by whom. The analytics dashboard surfaces skill adoption and dead skills at a glance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">Governance gates</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">Enforce metadata rules: required tags, version format, license compliance. Skills that fail governance checks are flagged in the dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">Version history</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">Every skill change is tracked via git history. See what changed, when, and by whom — right alongside the usage data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">Quality scores</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">Measure whether skills improve outcomes. Fewer errors, faster completions, higher acceptance rates — quantified and ranked.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--code-bg)]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent-text)]"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 21V9"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-[var(--text-lg)] font-semibold">Self-host everything</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">PostgreSQL + Astro SSR. Your skill data and usage analytics stay on your infrastructure — no cloud telemetry unless you opt in.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
